	   <tr><td colspan=2>On the Bertoxx server,I got picked up for a Naggie raid tonight...I was their only shaman.Key to this guy is people and good buffs/resists.He hits very hard.I recall him triple attacking a friend for 280(wasnt pleasant)and every 10 to 15 seconds he would do one of his famous "AoEs".One being a AoE fear.The other being a fire AoE that hurts bad if you don't have high FR.Was hitting me with it for anywhere from 125dmg to 525dmg each time.We had 7 groups(42peeps)of 46+ and half were tanks.Naggie went down fairly quick.Only lasted about a minute or so.I was main healer in group and I also had to slow him.I am Lvl 51 and he resisted 2 slows from right under him so stopped with the slows and just healed.Gotta have many nukers and melee to win this one.Also a bard comes in handy...didnt get fear on any of us cause bard had song playing so all MR was at 220 or higher for everyone.Ooops forgot to mention,Buffing takes a good hour depending on buffers could be less but as I said,I was the only shaman there.After you are buffed log to a chat room and wait till told to come back so buffs dont wear of course.Not much to it really...1)Get about 40 people or more.2)Clear Fire giants(some are hard)3)Buff out side at room outside of Naggie.4)After buffed log and come back when all have been buffed.5)Bumrush Naggie and fight him on BACK wall...very important or you will end up fighting on a bridge.6)Enjoy the great loot = )<br><br><br>Nalicar Niteglider<br>Lvl 51 Mystic<br>Holy Redemption<br>Bertoxxulous Server<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
